### Health endpoints — Makima API
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

@base_url = http://localhost:3000

### Health check
# Returns 200 if the service is running
GET {{base_url}}/health

### Readiness check
# Returns 200 if database is reachable, 503 otherwise
GET {{base_url}}/ready

### Health check with compression
# Request with Accept-Encoding header
GET {{base_url}}/health
Accept-Encoding: gzip

### OpenAPI JSON spec
# Returns the raw OpenAPI 3.0 JSON specification
GET {{base_url}}/api-doc/openapi.json

### Swagger UI
# Open in browser: {{base_url}}/swagger-ui
